  "subject": "Upgrade to Spring Boot 4 and update dependencies",
  "commit_message": "Upgrade to Spring Boot 4 and update dependencies\n\n- Upgrade Spring Boot from 3.5.14 to 4.0.6\n- Upgrade springdoc-openapi from 2.8.17 to 3.0.3\n- Bump json-schema-friend, json-schema-validator, bcpkix-fips, gRPC,\n  org.json, jackson-databind-nullable, opentelemetry-kafka-clients\n- Remove explicit commons-lang3 (now managed by Spring Boot BOM)\n- Add versions-maven-plugin to display dependency updates during validate\n- Fix Spring Boot 4 config: spring.mvc.converters → spring.http.converters\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-5592\nChange-Id: I50cb4f0efe4d25098f159eed40111daeda9a34a7\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\n",
